{"tid":370952,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"海燕37 秒前 10 【颱風追擊】1713號熱帶氣旋 天鴿 HATO（15W）#15","createTime":"2017-08-23T10:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T11:16:13.000Z","uid":44630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e12e83bc85c64ac53d8821a02c6d3217c38033d","tid":370952,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:37:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><img src=\"http://imgur.com/Pskei0w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FPskei0w.png&h=13bd482a&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>颱風追擊：熱帶氣旋天鴿</ins></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1713號熱帶氣旋 天鴿 HATO(15W)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">來源：日本<br />\n意義：天鴿星座（鴿子）</span></span></strong><br />\n【註】 發出颱風追擊帖，表示有熱帶氣旋在南海或西北太平洋一帶形成。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要張貼未經證實的風暴消息、使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。　以下圖片會自動更新，直至熱帶氣旋消散。<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">氣象台專頁現已登場</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/phDMEEd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FphDMEEd.png&h=c68c509c&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather&d=ox5U%2F7G%2FhUOIrXJuGdZiwDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7c133a72\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/OSjok6Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FOSjok6Z.png&h=fc73419e&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather&d=ox5U%2F7G%2FhUOIrXJuGdZiwDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6821c0eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather</a></span></em><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"fon